        "TileImage": "$($repository ce496422-f567-4a62-b2b0-d803ee249de4).Image",
        "Description": "Hello 47, this time OSHA has set its sights on the government. \r\rWorkplace safety is never more important than for our civil servants... and unfortunately they are also the most neglected.\r\rWittleton Creek is your destination. We have marked three civil servants who will experience an &quot;unofortunate workplace accident&quot;.\r\rGoodluck 47, and remember, we are making the worlds work places safer. One accident at a time.",
